source.name: Veterans Affairs Veteran Population Model - National Level Estimates and Projections
source.description: VetPop2007 is VA's latest official estimate and projection of the veteran population and their characteristics from 4/1/2000 to 9/30/2036, projected as of 9/30/2006.  This dataset contains the estimate and projection at the national level by 4 year age group, race, gender, and period of service.  There is one record for each unique combination of the variables for each date with the corresponding number of veterans estimated or projected at that date.
